Prodajemo trosoban stan koji se nalazi na 4. od 6 katova uredne i održavane stambene zgrade s LIFTOM na Vrbanima II. Zgrada je izgrađena 2008. godine te je PROTUPOTRESNA.
Stan ima 68,61 neto korisne površine m2 +  pripadajuće spremište u podrumu 2,42 m2.
Stan se sastoji od predulaza, hodnika, dvije spavaće sobe, dnevnog boravka s blagovaonom, kuhinje, kupaonice, dodatnog toaleta i loggie.
Grijanje je centralno etažno plinsko, a u stanu je postavljen i klima uređaj.
Stolarija je drvena, a vrata su protuprovalna.
Sva brojila su odvojena.
Stan gleda na zapadnu stranu.
Ispred zgrade nalazi se besplatan parking.
Autobusna stanica udaljena je 2 minute od zgrade, do tramvajskog stajališta potrebno je 5 minuta, blizina trgovina, osnovne škole, doma zdravlja te svih ostalih sadržaja potrebnih za život.
 
For Sale - Three-Room Apartment 71 m² - Vrbani, Cirkovljanska
Take a virtual tour of the property at the following link: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=kuP8Gumkdt9
We are selling a three-room apartment located on the 4th of 6 floors of a neat and well-maintained residential building with an ELEVATOR in Vrbani II. The building was built in 2008 and is EARTHQUAKE RESISTANT.
The apartment has a net usable area of 68.61 m² + a storage room in the basement of 2.42 m².
The apartment consists of an entrance hall, hallway, two bedrooms, living room with dining area, kitchen, bathroom, additional toilet, and loggia.
Heating is central gas heating, and an air conditioning unit is installed in the apartment.
The carpentry is wooden, and the doors are burglar-proof.
All meters are separate.
The apartment faces the west side.
There is free parking in front of the building.
The bus stop is 2 minutes away from the building, the tram stop is 5 minutes away, and there are shops, an elementary school, a health center, and all other amenities needed for living nearby.
 
 
