97-b643-aa7c0e978515.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/70c8fd82-77dd-440f-b856-df950d6d487f.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/a7ef8dd1-669f-40a3-99dd-806ebf853dab.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/81bee63f-3b29-4f04-a577-2d81b1832407.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/ec1a235b-8f35-438a-8a3b-38e7883730d3.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/5666f6b0-6696-421b-95eb-ef46229ad864.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/bd4a48d6-1013-490f-80ad-36c333013fa5.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/8a18578f-07dc-4cf3-b6f6-dccaae0ce8dd.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/ef8fac62-af64-495a-a732-5e42b8923cd7/a7052c5d-850c-44af-85bf-cdf7c8bf670c.jpg"}','Agencija Zagreb4U Vam predstavlja prostran stan u samom srcu Zagreb, smješten na drugom katu uredne stambene zgrade bez lifta. Ukupna površina stana iznosi 128 m², a dodatnu vrijednost daju dva balkona.
 
VIRTUALNA ŠETNJA: u izradi
 
Stan se sastoji od ulaznog hodnika, tri velike i svijetle sobe, od kojih jedna ima izlaz na balkon s pogledom na ulicu. U nastavku se nalazi kuhinja s izlazom na drugi balkon koji je orijentiran na mirno dvorište. Stan također ima jednu kupaonicu i zaseban toalet.
 
Posebna prednost ove nekretnine je dodatni prostor u suterenu površine cca 40 m², koji uz manje preinake ima potencijal za prenamjenu u zasebnu stambenu jedinicu (garsonijeru), što ovu nekretninu čini izuzetno zanimljivom investicijskom prilikom. Trenutno taj prostor nije etažnom vlasništvu vlasnika samog stana.
 
Zgrada je 2025. godine prošla konstrukcijsku obnovu, pri čemu su zidovi ojačani, što dodatno doprinosi sigurnosti i dugoročnoj vrijednosti nekretnine.
 
Lokacija je iznimno atraktivna – stan se nalazi u centru grada, s odličnom prometnom povezanošću i neposrednom blizinom javnog prijevoza (1 minuta hoda), kao i svih sadržaja potrebnih za ugodan život.
 
Preporuka agencije.
 
Agencijska provizija od kupca: 3% + PDV.
 
 --------------------------------------------------------------------
ENGLISH:
Zagreb4U Agency presents a spacious apartment in the very heart of Zagreb, located on the second floor of a well-maintained residential building without an elevator. The total area of the apartment is 128 m², with additional value provided by two balconies.
 
VIRTUAL TOUR: in making
 
The apartment consists of an entrance hall, three large and bright rooms, one of which has access to a balcony overlooking the street. The kitchen follows, with access to a second balcony facing a quiet courtyard. The apartment also includes one bathroom and a separate toilet.
 
A particular advantage of this property is an additional basement space of approximately 40 m², which, with minor modifications, has the potential to be converted into a separate residential unit (studio apartment), making this property an excellent investment opportunity. Please note that this space is currently not registered as a separate ownership unit of the apartment.
 
The building underwent structural renovation in 2025, during which the walls were reinforced, contributing to the safety and long-term value of the property.
 
The location is highly attractive – the apartment is situated in the city center, with excellent transport connections and immediate proximity to public transport (1-minute walk), as well as all amenities necessary for comfortable living.
 
Agency recommendation.
 
Agency commission from buyer: 3% + VAT.

Darko Zimić
Mob: +385 95 3512 309
