AGENT: Darko 095 351 2309 ili darko@zagreb4u.com
 
AGENCIJSKA PROVIZIJA OD NAJMOPRIMCA: 1 MJESEČNA NAJAMNINA + PDV
 
---------------------------------------------------------
 
AVAILABLE FROM MAY 1ST 2026
 
Zagreb4U Agency presents you a 2-bedroom apartment (85 m2) on the high ground floor of a small residential building, without an elevator, Srebrnjak.
 
VIRTUAL WALK: https://www.360.zagreb4u.com/4014/ 
 
It consists of two bedrooms (plan is to replace older wardrobe in one room with more modern one), one of which has a balcony, a living room, a kitchen with a dining room leading to a large terrace of approximately 36 m2, a bathroom and a toilet.
 
The apartment has one outdoor uncovered parking space in the building yard that is fenced. Free parking on the street.
 
Bus stop nearby.
 
The apartment is air-conditioned, has a 2-in-1 washing machine and dryer, and a dishwasher. It is possible to arrange the use of a part of the storage room in the garage.
 
