KNEŽIJA - ODMAH KOD SAVSKE

Stan se nalazi na PETOM (5.) katu u zgradi sa dizalom.

NAPOMENA: GARAŽA (16.00 m2) JE URAČUNATA U CIJENU NAJAMNINE

STAN SE SASTOJI od ulaznog prostora zaštićenog protuprovalnim vratima i namještenog vrlo prostranim ugradbenim garderobnim ormarom, kuhinje, klimatiziranog dnevnog boravka sa blagovaonicom u jednoj funkcionalnoj cjelini i IZLAZOM NA TERASU, spavaće sobe s bračnim ležajem i garderobni ormarom, treće sobe s jednostrukim ležajem, radnim stolom sa stolicom i garderobnim ormarom, kupaonice s tuš kabinom i WC-om, DVIJE (2) TERASE i GARAŽE (16.00 m2). 

Stan je klimatiziran, a grijanje je centralno etažno plinsko.

U stanu su ugrađena zasebna brojila za očitavanje utroška vode, plina i struje - minimalni troškovi režija - plaćanje prema stvarnoj, kontroliranoj potrošnji.

STAN JE OPREMLJEN:
- sat/kabl/TV, protuprovalna vrata, klima uređaj,  LED TV, telefonski priključak, UVEDEN INTERNET  (A1), hladnjak s ledenicom, ugradbeni štednjak,  perilica rublja, PVC stolarija

- UGOVOR O NAJMU STANA

- AGENCIJSKA PROVIZIJA : 1 NAJAMNINA

- STAN JE DOSTUPAN ZA NAJAM ODMAH

Poštovani najmoprimci,

zahvaljujemo Vam na povjerenju koje nam ukazujete punih 36 godina, prepoznajući naše profesionalne standarde, etičnost i izvrsnost u poslovanju, te najbolji omjer cijene i kvalitete na tržištu.

Sve nekretnine iz naše ponude su pravno provjerene i dostupne za najam odmah, a naše stručno i ljubazno osoblje će sa zadovoljstvom odgovoriti na sva Vaša pitanja.

MI OPRAVDAVAMO VAŠE POVJERENJE          

ENGLISH
--------------------------------------------------
THREE-BEDROOM FURNISHED APARTMENT + TWO (2) TERRACES + GARAGE (16.00 m2)

KNEŽIJA - RIGHT NEAR SAVSKA

The apartment is located on the FIFTH (5th) floor of a building with an elevator.

NOTE: GARAGE (16.00 m2) IS INCLUDED IN THE RENTAL PRICE

THE APARTMENT CONSISTS of an entrance area protected by a burglar-proof door and furnished with a very spacious built-in wardrobe, kitchen, air-conditioned living room with dining room in one functional unit and EXIT TO THE TERRACE, bedroom with double bed and wardrobe, third bedroom with single bed, desk with chair and wardrobe, bathroom with shower and toilet, TWO (2) TERRACES and GARAGE (16.00 m2).

The apartment is air-conditioned, and the heating is central gas.

The apartment has separate meters for reading water, gas and electricity consumption - minimal utility costs - payment according to actual, controlled consumption.

THE APARTMENT IS EQUIPPED WITH:
- satellite/cable/TV, security door, air conditioning, LED TV, telephone connection, INTERNET (A1), refrigerator with freezer, built-in stove, washing machine, PVC joinery

- APARTMENT RENTAL AGREEMENT

- AGENCY COMMISSION: 1 RENT

- THE APARTMENT IS AVAILABLE FOR RENT IMMEDIATELY

Dear tenants,

we thank you for the trust you have shown us for 36 years, recognizing our professional standards, ethics and excellence in business, and the best price-quality ratio on the market.

All properties from our offer are legally verified and available for rent immediately, and our professional and friendly staff will be happy to answer all your questions.

WE JUSTIFY YOUR TRUST',true) ON CONFLICT (source,external_id) DO NOTHING;
