fe2b8961/562e09a8-afaa-4f3d-bd21-3a6ac9d86442.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/b46daec2-0296-4f06-898a-c9ebfe2b8961/872e615b-8d76-4ff3-8259-8fd1d6745eeb.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/b46daec2-0296-4f06-898a-c9ebfe2b8961/4f5d74e8-35ff-464d-ba93-2bf4a6361135.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/b46daec2-0296-4f06-898a-c9ebfe2b8961/7cc8fbfc-48e2-4f3f-a796-d39a578398f1.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/b46daec2-0296-4f06-898a-c9ebfe2b8961/df94ffc9-b866-401d-b67b-08f325a8dc72.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/b46daec2-0296-4f06-898a-c9ebfe2b8961/434809c5-369a-4ca7-b62f-a60873518727.jpg"}','Iznajmljuje se ugodan, svjetao, luksuzno namjesten i potpuno opremljen  noviji stan 45m2 u maloj i mirnoj zgradi, na atraktivnoj lokaciji. Stan se nalazi u Stolačkoj ulici, 100m od Savske i tramvaja i autobusa (Savski most) i u blizini svih potrebnih sadržaja za ugodan život. 
U neposrednoj blizini je osnovna škola, vrtić, pošta, dom zdravlja i laboratorij, razni dućani (Spar, Lidl, Konzum, Bipa, DM, Muller), Jarun, Mladost, rijeka Sava . . . 

Stan se iznajmljuje na duže vrijeme, ozbiljnoj osobi, nepušaču, poslovnim ljudima, bez kućnih ljubimaca. Stan posjeduje i pripadajuce vanjsko parkirno mjesto koje je pod video nadzorom, kao i ulaz u zgradu.
Kao što se može vidjeti na slikama stan je kao nov, svježe okrečen, čist, miriše na novo, potpuno namjesten, odmah useljiv i opremljen novim uređajima, uključujući perilicu za posuđe, perilicu za rublje, hladnjak+zamrzivač, štednjak, mikrovalna, klima uređaj, 2 TV-a, mini stereo uređaj, usisivač, daska za peglanje, pegla . . . . 


Sve rezije su individualne, izuzetno male i plaćaju se po potrošnji (40 eura je mjesečni paušal za sve), a zimi gotovo da nije potrebno grijanje, jer je stan orijentiran na jug i pun je sunca i prirodnog svjetla. 


Obavezan je i polog od 800 eura. 
Cijena najma je 700 eura. 

Sve dodatne informacije na tel. 091 522 1950



Pleasant, bright, luxuriously furnished and fully equipped newer apartment of 45m2 in a small and quiet building, in an attractive location for rent. The apartment is located in Stolačka street, 100m from Savska street and trams and buses (Savski most) and close to all necessary amenities for a comfortable and pleasant life. 
In the immediate vicinity is an elementary school, kindergarten, post office, health center and laboratory, various shops (Spar, Lidl, Konzum, Bipa, DM, Muller), lake Jarun, sport center Mladost, the Sava river. . . 

The apartment is intended for a long time rent, to a serious person/ business people, non smoker, without pets. The apartment also has an outdoor parking space that is under video surveillance, as well as the entrance to the building.
As you can see in the pictures, the apartment is like brand new, freshly painted, clean, smells new, fully furnished and ready to move in immediately. Apartment is equipped with new appliances, including a dishwasher, washing machine, fridge + freezer, stove, microwave, air conditioning, 2 TVs, mini stereo, vacuum cleaner, iron, ironing board. . . . 

All utilities are individual, extremely small and paid according to consumption (40 euros is a basic monthly flat rate for everything + consumption), and in winter there is almost no need for heating, because the apartment is oriented to the south and is full of sun and natural light. 

A deposit of 800 euros is also required. 
The rental price is 700 euros. 

For any additional information, call 091 522 1950',true) ON CONFLICT (source,external_id) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO listings (external_id,source,url,title,deal_type,price,currency,area_m2,rooms,floor,total_floors,year_built,furnished,address,city,latitude,longitude,images,description,is_active) VALUES ('7305838','index-hr','https://www.index.hr/oglasi/nekretnine/najam-stanova/oglas/tresnjevka-najam-garsonijere/7305838','TREŠNJEVKA, NAJAM GARSONIJERE','rent',400.0,'EUR',17.25,NULL,1,1,NULL,NULL,'Trešnjevka - Sjever, Trešnjevka','Zagreb',45.8018377,15.9416367,'{"https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/38c6ddd2-cb0f-4dc7-b5ee-ef2c0bf989be.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/e09f8803-3a2f-4a93-90cf-e118df092104.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/172660e5-d6a8-4d95-94c3-d2ea0877700b.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/8da62a97-7205-43bf-a52f-34acd15a9d1f.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/631e3cbf-b436-4304-a4fb-ca94eb6d93e4.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/4bff304b-b6f9-4593-a8c1-586d3c83d510.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/5cc512bc-d25a-4a73-8976-c572e0420dab.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/7da52f78-ed32-4a93-b0f7-da9a717f6b1a.jpg","https://www.index.hr/oglasi/api/image/direct/fd8e6460-7eea-4b2a-0ff4-08de59ca39bd/10d9ca18-d77f-490b-929e-c4e951023cec.jpg"}','Iznajmljuje se mala, ali vrlo skladna i funkcionalna garsonijera na jednoj od najtraženijih lokacija – Trešnjevka.

Stan je idealan za samca ili par koji traže praktičan i ugodan prostor za život. Smješten je na izvrsnoj lokaciji s odličnom povezanošću javnim prijevozom te u neposrednoj blizini svih potrebnih sadržaja poput trgovina, kafića, restorana i drugih usluga.

Garsonijera je u potpunosti namještena i opremljena svim osnovnim aparatima, što omogućuje ugodan i jednostavan svakodnevni život bez dodatnih ulaganja. Prostor je dobro organiziran i maksimalno iskorišten.

Grijanje i hlađenje osigurani su putem klima uređaja, a režijski troškovi su niski i plaćaju se odvojeno prema potrošnji.

