Iznajmljuje se jednoetažni stan površine 35 m2 a koji se sastoji od: ulaznog prostora, kuhinje, dnevni boravak + spavaća soba, kupaonice. Stan se nalazi u održavanoj stambenoj zgradi koja je smještena u odličnoj lokaciji u centru Trešnjevke te obiluje društvenim i životnim sadržajima. Tramvajske i autobusne linije redovito prometuju prema ostatku naselje ali i prema Trešnjevki jug, Črnomercu, okretištu Savski most, centru grada i prema Novom Zagrebu.

Uvjeti najma: 
Ugovor na minimum godinu dana.
Osim najamnine plaća se i depozit u visini od jedne mjesečne najamnine.
Kućni ljubimci nisu dozvoljeni.

Stan se može pogledati prema dogovoru, a useljiv je odmah.

For more information and to arrange a viewing, please contact us via SMS or WhatsApp at 0913572196, or by email at pedja@san-nekretnine.hr. When sending your inquiry, please include the ad link, the ad reference number, or a brief description of the property.

A single-story apartment of 35 m2 is available for rent, consisting of: entrance area, kitchen, living room + bedroom, and a bathroom. The apartment is located in a well-maintained residential building situated in an excellent location in the center of Trešnjevka, close to all social and lifestyle amenities. Tram and bus lines run regularly to the rest of the neighborhood, as well as towards Trešnjevka South, Črnomerec, the Savski Most terminal, the city center, and Novi Zagreb.

Rental conditions:
Minimum one-year contract.
In addition to the rent, a deposit equal to one month''s rent is required.
Pets are not allowed.

The apartment can be viewed by appointment and is available for immediate move-in.

